              (the field the visibility condition reads for "Assigned only")
            - ../dictionary/x_casemgmt_case_assigned_group.xml
              (the field the visibility condition reads for "Assigned only")
            - ../dictionary/x_casemgmt_case_task_status.xml
              (the field the Script Include's getOpenTaskCountForCase
               filters on; required so the column exists)
            - ../dictionary/x_casemgmt_case_task_case.xml
