          - ../script_includes/x_casemgmt_CaseTransitionValidator.xml
            (the central transition-guard helper; this UI Action's
             canTransitionToResolved call delegates to its method of
             the same name; the SAME Script Include holds the verbatim
             AAP Section 0.7.4 error message string)
          - ../flows/sub_flows/validate_resolved_transition.xml
            (the Flow Designer subflow that runs the SAME guard via
